emoving a flag's conditional gate makes it non-independent; coupling two flags in one condition makes both non-independent; flipping over_budget:true breaks the auto-stop detection). Realtime not regressed (NOT deployed; live b189d3cc0703). Cost: production 0 (NOT_DEPLOYED); recurring $0/mo (free tier); 1 read-only GET. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
